data.description: Welcome Home! This home is stunning, spacious and so much potential for a forever home.  The home features vaulted ceilings and beautiful natural sunlight! THE HOME SITS ON A LARGE LOT ON A CUL-DE-SAC IN THE POINT AT GLENEAGLE SUBDIVISION! YOUR JOURNEY THROUGH THIS HOME BEGINS IN THE FORMAL LIVING ROOM AND DINING ROOM.  The Kitchen has a gorgeous center island that opens up into large family room that is perfect for entertaining. Sliding glass doors invite you and yours to outdoor fun in the sun.  Awesome concrete paver patio.  As you float upstairs viewing the vaulted ceiling for a very airy feel, you will arrive at the master suite that has a double sink vanity, huge soaking tub & separate shower!  This two-story home has 4 BRs, 3 BA, BONUS ROOM, 2-Car Garage and full basement.  The Partially finished FULL basement offers a wealth of potential to create another living quarters or a mega entertainment area.  All Appliances will stay. This property is being SOLD AS-IS. Motivated Seller!!
